HELP SYSSORT_N                                      Steve Knight, Oct 91

    syssort_n( N, P ) -> N

This procedure sorts the N items on the stack using a `less-than' predicate P.
Based on *SYSSORT, this procedure is useful for sorting non-list data
structures.

    syssort_n( 'fred'.deststring, nonop < ).consstring =>
    ** defr
